member.name: IsolatedAppLauncherTelemetryParameters
member.summary: A struct that provides telemetry parameters to be used when launching an app inside the container.

member.name: IsolatedAppLauncherTelemetryParameters.EnableForLaunch
member.summary: The EnableForLaunch field is a boolean value that indicates whether telemetry is enabled for the launch.

member.name: IsolatedAppLauncherTelemetryParameters.CorrelationGUID
member.summary: The CorrelationGUID field is a GUID that is used to correlate telemetry events.
